@startuml pipeline-docs

skinparam defaultFontName Liberation Sans
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

skinparam activity {
  BorderColor #003087
  BackgroundColor #EEF3FA
  FontColor #003087
  StartColor #003087
  EndColor #003087
  BarColor #003087
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9E6
  BorderColor #C8A400
  FontColor #555555
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color #333333
  FontColor #555555
  FontSize 9
}

note
  docs.yml · Triggers: push / PR → main (tfg-doc/** paths) · workflow_dispatch
  release and pages both depend on build; they run in parallel after it completes.
end note

|build|
start
:Checkout\n(actions/checkout@v4);
:Setup Typst\n(typst-community/setup-typst@v3);
:Install Roboto font\n(apt-get install fonts-roboto-unhinted);
:Compile document\n(typst compile tfg-doc/main.typ tfg-doc/main.pdf);
:Upload PDF artifact\n(actions/upload-artifact@v4 → tfg-doc-pdf);

fork

|release — needs: build|
:Download PDF artifact;
:Publish GitHub Release\n(tag: docs-latest, rolling — URL never changes);

note right
  The docs-latest tag is reused
  on every run, keeping a single
  stable download URL.
end note

fork again

|pages — needs: build|
:Download PDF artifact;
:Add redirect index.html\n(meta refresh → main.pdf);
:Upload pages artifact\n(actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3);
:Deploy to GitHub Pages\n(actions/deploy-pages@v4);

end fork

stop

@enduml
